FBIS3-44587 "drchi004_v_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 TAIWAN Official: Taipei To Alter Mainland Trade Policy OW0601144894 Taipei Voice of Free China in English 0200 GMT 6 Jan 94 OW0601144894 Taipei Voice of Free China Language: English Article Type:BFN [From the "News" program] [Text] Chairman of the Executive Yuan's Mainland Affairs Council [MAC] Huang Kun-hui on Wednesday [5 December] morning said that in order to maintain Taiwan's competitive edge, the government will in the future take a more liberalized stand on trade and economic dealings between the two sides of the Taiwan Strait. However, he said that it did not mark a significant change in government policy.
